      <title>关税威胁供应，美国石油涨幅超过全球油价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-gains-outpace-global-benchmark-on-trump-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布征收关税，威胁到美国两大外国供应国的石油供应后，美国原油基准价格的涨幅超过其他石油市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-gains-outpace-global-benchmark-on-trump-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
